    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="626db-102">一般而言，當建立新的資料來源類別階層式資料和伴隨的設計工具，則會繼承<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner>類別，而不是實作<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner>介面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="626db-102">Typically, when creating a new data source class for hierarchical data and an accompanying designer, you would inherit the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner> class rather than implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner> interface.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
