        <block subset="none" type="overrides">
          <para>
            <span data-ttu-id="626db-121">如果您實作<see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner" />永遠不會變更介面來建立您自己的資料來源和結構描述，<see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.CanRefreshSchema" />屬性應該會一律傳回<see langword="false" />和<see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema(System.Boolean)" />方法應該會引發<see cref="T:System.NotSupportedException" />。</span>
            <span class="sxs-lookup">
              <span data-stu-id="626db-121">If you implement the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner" /> interface to create your own data source and the schema will never change, the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.CanRefreshSchema" /> property should always return <see langword="false" /> and the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema(System.Boolean)" /> method should raise a <see cref="T:System.NotSupportedException" />.</span>
            </span>
            <span data-ttu-id="626db-122">一般而言，如果<see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema(System.Boolean)" />因使用者動作而設計主應用程式會呼叫<paramref name="preferSilent" />參數便是<see langword="false" />，因為預期使用者會收到通知的重新整理結構描述的任何問題。</span>
