              <span data-stu-id="626db-122">Typically, if the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema(System.Boolean)" /> is called by the design host as a result of user action, the <paramref name="preferSilent" /> parameter would be <see langword="false" />, because the user would expect to be notified of any problems with refreshing the schema.</span>
