            <span class="sxs-lookup">
              <span data-stu-id="626db-123">But, if the schema is refreshed implicitly, such as after a call to the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.Configure" /> method, or if the refreshing process involves a number of steps, <paramref name="preferSilent" /> should be set to <see langword="true" />.</span>
